### 10.6 What We Do NOT Steal (And Why)

| Cookbook Item | Why We Skip It |
|---|---|
| Stable Diffusion image generation | Not relevant to agent certification |
| Wikipedia RAG | We use domain-specific task JSONs, not free-text retrieval |
| Generic customer service agent patterns | We inherit from our existing ReAct/Reflection agents |

Everything not listed above is either in our Tier 1-3 plan or irrelevant to agent certification. Nothing is ignored; everything is deliberately categorized.
